General.Name: L.A. Gear Inc
General.Description: L.A. Gear, Inc. provides shoes for men, women, and kids. It offers its products through retailers. The company was formerly known as Good Times, Inc. and changed its name to L.A. Gear, Inc. in 1982. The company was founded in 1979 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
General.Address: 1800 Avenue of the Stars, Los Angeles, CA, United States, 90067
